      <title>尼日利亚改造后两周内吸引了 10 亿美元资金流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-09/nigeria-attracts-1-billion-of-inflows-in-two-weeks-since-revamp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚央行行长奥拉耶米·卡多佐 (Olayemi Cardoso) 表示，随着央行努力稳定该国饱受打击的货币，市场信心有所改善，过去两周尼日利亚外汇市场吸引了超过 10 亿美元的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-09/nigeria-attracts-1-billion-of-inflows-in-two-weeks-since-revamp</guid>
